# Copy to `.env.mobile` (gitignored) and set the ABSOLUTE backend URL for the mobile build.
# The mobile app runs from a WebView origin, so it cannot use the relative "/api/v1" the
# web deployment uses — it needs a full host it can reach over the network.
#
# Build the mobile web bundle with:  npm run build:mobile   (loads this file via --mode mobile)
#
# Examples:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://jps.example.com/api/v1        # production (HTTPS, recommended)
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.50:3000/api/v1       # pilot on a private IP (cleartext)
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://YOUR_API_HOST/api/v1
